name: Electronauts
summary: Ever wanted to ride the vibes of a top DJ playing a packed festival’s main stage? Here’s your chance to shine: all it takes to be an Electronaut is the passion to become one with the beat. Create music with confidence, no matter your skill level, as you make music magic in this VR-exclusive experience featuring 80-plus songs from over 80 top artists across EDM, hip hop, trap, and countless other genres.
